data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.75% VA LOAN!!!, You DON'T have to be a veteran!!!!! Monthly Payment of approximately $7K at 2.75%, $12k a month at today's mortgage rates, SAVE $5K a Month!!!! Absolutely remarkable custom Toll Brothers Henley Model home located in the coveted Patuxent Chase community sparing no expense offering the top-of-line builder’s package, plus every superior custom upgrade imaginable! Upgrades include: luxury flooring, plush carpeting, granite counters, upper level HVAC, water heater, and so much more! Boasting magnificent design elements, custom lighting and molding, dual stairs, and an exceptional open floor plan! Grand two story foyer adorned with an elegant curved staircase appointed with decorative iron balusters. Opposing formal living and dining rooms complemented with a tray ceiling, lighted wall feature, stone accent wall, chair railing, and wainscoting. Sensational two story family room graced with floor to ceiling sunbathed windows and a stone accented wood burning fireplace. Prepare delectable meals in the chef inspired custom kitchen offering modern elegance yet comfort and style with exceptional granite counters, tile backsplash, professional grade appliances, center-island, breakfast bar, gas cooking, walk in pantry, pendant lighting, planning station, a casual dining area, and patio access. A main level office with custom built ins, amazing powder room, laundry room, and an arrival center conclude the masterfully designed main level. A secondary staircase gives access from the kitchen to the upper level. Enter into the spectacular primary bedroom suite highlighted with a three sided fireplace for ambiance, an inviting sitting room with a fireplace, and a walk in closet. The luxurious en suite bath features a tray ceiling, separate vanities, Jacuzzi, two water closets, separate oversized shower with seating and a huge walk in closet. Three additional graciously sized en suite bedrooms complete the upper level sleeping quarters. Continue downstairs to the truly impressive lower level emphasizing a massive recreation room, custom bar with granite, wine cellar, exercise area, a fifth bedroom, media room, full bath; and walkout stair access. Enjoy hosting summer barbecues from the comfort of the outdoor paradise graced with a fireplace, custom bar with a built in grill, expansive patio, pergola, professionally landscaped grounds and mature trees. Located minutes from Hobbit’s Glen Golf Club for the avid golf enthusiast, this home embodies perfection! Simply a must see!
